snippet.title: IGN News
snippet.description: IGN News is the best place to find breaking updates on all your favorite video games, movies, TV shows and tech gadgets. We post breaking news all throughout the day and wrap up the biggest stories with The Daily Fix. Wanna know what games were announced, what super heroes were killed off, and every single news tidbit about Star Wars ever!? Subscribe today and don't miss a thing.
